  "body": "**Meeting Date/Time: Thursday 2021/4/1 at 13:00 UTC**\r\n**Meeting Duration 90 minutes**\r\n\r\n### Agenda\r\n- Rayonism announcement ☀️ \r\n  - http://rayonism.io\r\n- Consensus Upgrade discussion\r\n    - Application-layer\r\n        - design doc https://hackmd.io/@n0ble/ethereum_consensus_upgrade_mainnet_perspective\r\n        - new block format\r\n        - block processing and fork choice\r\n        - interaction between consensus and application layers\r\n        - state and block sync\r\n        - transition process\r\n        - next steps\r\n    - Consensus-layer\r\n        - PR https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2257\r\n        - TODO https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/issues/2280\r\n        - include `pow_block.timestamp` into validity conditions\r\n        - opaque transactions\r\n        - max block size in relation to `ApplicationPayload`\r\n        - more fields in the `ApplicationPayload`, consider including `parent_hash`, `number`, PR https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/2295\r\n        - eliminate `uint256` on the beacon chain side; currently used as a type for total difficulty\r\n- Open discussions\r\n",
